aspect: Transiting Venus is Trine your Natal Moon
description: This is an excellent time for socializing and connecting with others. You may feel emotionally balanced and find it easy to express your feelings. Romance and creative pursuits are favored during this transit.

aspect: Transiting Mercury is Sextile your Natal Jupiter
description: Your mind is sharp and optimistic now. This is a great time for learning, teaching, or engaging in intellectual discussions. Travel and expansion of your horizons are also highlighted.

aspect: Transiting Sun is Square your Natal Saturn
description: You may feel challenged by authority figures or external limitations during this period. Patience and persistence are required. Use this time to work through obstacles with discipline and maturity.

aspect: Transiting Mars is Sextile your Natal Pluto
description: During this transit, you may dare to transform something about yourself; your appearance, personal surroundings or your relationship with another or group of people. You can achieve results now through perseverance and persistence.

aspect: Transiting Jupiter is Trine your Natal Venus
description: This is a time of good fortune in love and financial matters. You may feel generous and optimistic. Social activities and artistic pursuits are especially rewarding now.
